[The autumn migration of wild birds has left a trail of death in its wake. Avian influenza continues its death march.

Diligent attention to excellent biosecurity of your birds, whether commercial or private, is exceptionally important.

Hopefully, this disease will soon be a thing of the past. - Mod.TG]
